Now encryption data at rest is enabled.

Create a new secrets as myapp-secret-2 and run below command where the ETCD will show the data or not.
ETCDCTL_API=3 etcdctl \
   --cacert=/etc/kubernetes/pki/etcd/ca.crt   \
   --cert=/etc/kubernetes/pki/etcd/server.crt \
